Uniform Child Custody Jurisdiction and E.raw_text: Uniform Child Custody Jurisdiction and Enforcement Act, G.L. c. 209B
Uniform Child Custody Jurisdiction and E.proposition: This Court has jurisdiction over this matter pursuant to Massachusetts law governing custody, parenting schedules and the Uniform Child Custody Jurisdiction and Enforcement Act, G.L. c. 209B, because the parties and children are domiciled in Massachusetts and the Probate and Family Court entered the existing custody/parenting order.
